OL,3,GYorkshire & Humber
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FA cloudy start, with some light
OL,6,Foutbreaks of rain moving south across
OL,7,Fthe region during the morning.
OL,8,FBecoming brighter with sunny spells
OL,9,Fand perhaps the odd shower during the
OL,10,Fafternoon. Blustery, and feeling cold
OL,11,Ffor the time of year.
OL,12,
OL,13,CTonight:FAny showers fading during the
OL,14,Fevening, with clear skies developing
OL,15,Ffor a time. However, further showers
OL,16,Fwill arrive across the region during
OL,17,Fthe overnight period, these heavy and
OL,18,Fblustery.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
