OL,3,GYorkshire & Humber
OL,4,
OL,5,CWednesday:FA day of sunny spells and
OL,6,Fblustery showers, some of the showers
OL,7,Fturning locally heavy with hail and
OL,8,Fthunder. Feeling rather cold with
OL,9,Ftemperatures below normal.
OL,10,
OL,11,COutlook for Thursday to Saturday:
OL,12,FFurther heavy showers likely on
OL,13,FThursday and Friday, which also carry
OL,14,Fa risk of thunder. Some sunny spells
OL,15,Fin the mix too. Drier and brighter on
OL,16,FSaturday.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
